- extends "base.jade"

- block content
  .hero-unit
    h1 Deep-tac-toe game
    p Yo, dawg!
    p.
      I've heard you like tictactoe, so I've put tictactoe in your
      tictactoe so you can play while you play
  
  .row
    .span4
      h2 Play with your friend!
      p Go find one if you need!
      p
        a.btn(href='/hotseat') Hotseat game

    .span4
      h2 Play online!
      p Play over large network called Internets.
      p
        a.btn(href='/network') Network game

    .span4
      h2 Fork me on GitHub
      p You'd like that.
      p
        a.btn(href='https://github.com/Volshebnyi/python-deeptactoe') Fork me on GitHub
